<center><b>Glassmaking</b><br><br><i>Glassmaking is only available to RuneScape members.<br>
Please <a href="/members" class=c>subscribe</a> to get this feature.</i><br><br></center>

<table>
<tr><td valign=top><p>To make some glass, you will first need to get some seaweed. 
This can be obtained by big net fishing, or found on Entrana Island. 
Heat the seaweed to get soda ash. <br><br>Then use a bucket on a sandpit, to 
get a bucket of sand. With both soda ash and sand in your inventory, 
you can then use a furnace on either one to make molten glass.</td>
<td><img src="/img/rs2/manual/crafting/sandpit.gif" width=153 height=135></td></tr></table>
<p>Use this molten glass with a glass-blowing pipe, which can also be found
on Entrana. You will then be asked what object you would like to make.
