<center><b>Battlestaffs</b><br><p>
<i>Battlestaff crafting is only available to RuneScape members.<br>
Please <a href="/members" class=c>subscribe</a> to get this feature.</i><br><br></center>

<p>First get an unpowered orb (see glassmaking).

<p>You will need to enchant the orb. You can make fire orbs, earth orbs, water orbs and air orbs.
Take an orb to a magic obelisk (either the obelisk of air, the obelisk of earth, the obelisk of water or the obelisk of fire) and cast the appropriate orb enchantment spell on the obelisk.
This requires a high magic level (see <a href="/rs2/skills/magic" class=c>magic guide</a>).
The obelisks are not in easily accesible areas.

<p>Then buy a battlestaff from a staff shop on a members server. Use the battlestaff with a charged orb to make an elemental battlestaff. 
